  %section.width
    %div
      %h2 The Employer Network
      %p The Portland Code School Employer Network is free to join and provides you with exclusive opportunities to meet our students in order to know them. If you meet a student you want on your team, at the end of the program, you can hire them.

      %h3 Be a Partner
      %p We listen to feedback and input from you to ensure we teach the skills you are hiring for and that the students we admit are the kinds of employees you want on your team.

      %h3 Build Relationships
      %p Take time to get to know our students. When it comes time to hire, you can ensure you find the best fit for your team. Students who get to know your company are more likely to be excited about working for you and be loyal, dedicated employees.

      %h3 Training and Ongoing Support
      %p We offer employer trainings on bringing junior developers up to speed after hiring and provide ongoing support for mentoring and evaluating new hires.
      %p
        %strong To join the Employer Network, send us:
      %ul
        %li The name and email address of a liason from your company
        %li A 100x100 image of your logo and a destination url
      %p
        %strong
          Email us at
          %a{:href => "mailto:employers@portlandcodeschool.com" } employers@portlandcodeschool.com
