      %p
        %strong Employer Network Training
      %p Attend our webinar training free to Employer Network members all about bringing a junior developer up to speed in just two weeks.

    %div
      %img{:src => "/images/en_badges/job_fair.jpg"}
      %p
        %strong Job Fair
      %p Come meet each of the students in week eight to find out if there is a new team member for your company among them.

    %div
      %img{:src => "/images/en_badges/host_a_hacker.jpg"}
      %p
        %strong Host a Hacker
      %p Get to know a student by hosting them one or two days a week in the final month of the program. See if they fit into your team dynamic by including them in team fun & social time on Fridays, let them get a feel for your office culture.

    %div
      %img{:src => "/images/en_badges/mentor_a_student.jpg"}
      %p
        %strong Mentor a Student
      %p Assign a team member to check in periodically with a student you are hosting to help with projects and to evaluate their technical ability and work style. Mentors can also help students by pairing to work on a bug or a feature in a prominent open source project.

